high_descs: Go to the counter behind you and to the right of the sink.
Pick up the egg closest to the wall.
Go to the microwave to your right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Go to the trash can behind you and next to the stove.
Place the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the trash.

high_descs: Pick up the rear potato next to the coffee machine.
Bring the potato to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the potato to the green trash can.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the plum on the right.
Turn right and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the plum in it, heat it up, and take the plum out of microwave.
Turn right, head towards the wall, turn right head towards the green bin on the floor.
Place the plum inside the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed up plum inside the green bin.
